\c 31
\s Kudanwa kwaBhezareri naOhoriabhu
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura naMozisi achiti:
\v 2 Ona, ndadana nezita Bhezareri mwanakomana waUri, mwanakomana waHuri, werudzi rwaJudha,
\v 3 uye ndamuzadza neMweya waMwari, muuchenjeri nemukunzwisisa nemuruzivo nemumabasa ese eunyanzvi,
\v 4 kuti aronge mano eunyanzvi, kubata negoridhe, uye nesirivha, uye nendarira,
\v 5 nemukufombora mabwe kuaisa, nemukufombora matanda, kubata mabasa ese.
\v 6 Uye ini, tarira ndapa pamwe naye Ohoriabhu mwanakomana waAhisamaki, werudzi rwaDhani; nemumoyo weumwe neumwe wemoyo wakachenjera ndakaisa uchenjeri, kuti vaite zvese zvandakakuraira,
\v 7 \add zvinoti\add*: Tende rekusangana, neareka yechipupuriro, nechigaro chengonichiri pamusoro payo, nenhumbi dzese dzetabhenakeri,
\v 8 netafura nemidziyo yayo, nechigadziko chemwenje chakazara nenhumbi dzacho dzese, nearitari yezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira,
\v 9 nearitari yezvipiriso zvinopiswa nenhumbi dzayo dzese, nedhishi nechigadziko charo,
\v 10 nenguvo dzezvirukwa, nenguvo tsvene dzaAroni mupristi, nenguvo dzevanakomana vake kushumira paupristi,
\v 11 namafuta okuzodza nawo, nezvinonhuhwira zvemiti inonaka zvapanzvimbo tsvene; vanofanira kuita zvese sezvandakakuraira.
\s Murairo wesabata
\p
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha wakataura naMozisi akati:
\v 13 Taura navana vaIsraeri, uti: Zvirokwazvo munofanira kuchengeta masabata angu; nokuti chiratidzo pakati pangu nemwi kusvikira kumarudzi enyu ese, muzive kuti ndini Jehovha unokuitai vatsvene.
\v 14 Naizvozvo chengetai sabata, nokuti idzvene kwamuri; ani nani unorizvidza ngaaurawe zvirokwazvo; nokuti ani nani unobata basa ripi neripi naro, munhu uyo ngaabviswe pakati porudzi rwake.
\v 15 Mabasa ese ngaabatwe namazuva matanhatu, asi zuva rechinomwe isabata rokuzorora kwazvo, idzvene kuna Jehovha; ani nani unobata basa ripi neripi nezuva resabata, ngaaurawe zvirokwazvo.
\v 16 Naizvozvo vana vaIsraeri vanofanira kuchengeta sabata, varangarire sabata kusvikira kumarudzi avo ese; ive sungano isingaperi.
\v 17 Chiratidzo pakati pangu navana vaIsraeri nokusingaperi; nokuti Jehovha wakaita denga nenyika namazuva matanhatu, akazorora nezuva rechinomwe, akasimbiswa.
\p
\v 18 Zvino wakati apedza kutaura naMozisi pagomo reSinai, akamupa mabwendefa maviri echipupuriro, mabwendefa amabwe akange akanyorwa neumwe waMwari.
